00:23:12,440 --> 00:23:14,590
Wanna spend some time with you.
Talk.

370
00:23:20,638 --> 00:23:22,838
- Is that my phone?
- Yeah, we must-- I got it.

371
00:23:23,316 --> 00:23:24,328
I got it. Hello?

372
00:23:25,517 --> 00:23:26,528
Who is this?

373
00:23:27,622 --> 00:23:29,152
