384
00:23:58,773 --> 00:24:01,069
- I gotta go.
- Wait! I'm sorry, wait!

385
00:24:01,082 --> 00:24:02,019
I don't have time, OK?

386
00:24:02,020 --> 00:24:04,578
I just wanna know who Billy was
