438
00:26:44,626 --> 00:26:45,665
Judges?

439
00:26:46,524 --> 00:26:47,933
Yeah, a clerk for one.

440
00:26:49,154 --> 00:26:50,182
Nitzberg.

441
00:26:51,158 --> 00:26:52,922
